property.value:
"BossStage" Parameter
0 "BossEnter": Loops until u trigger the cutscene. 1 "Cutscene" Plays a linear piece during the cutscene and moves in to a loop once the fight begins. 2 "Stage 1" transition into a new loop. 3 "Stage 2" New loop.
*The transitions between the loops happen instantly on the beat (drums, bass,rythm). Other instruments are crossfaded.
In the transitions there are on the synth stab track a sound that signals the stage change and it gets pitched up each transition.
The "ProgressionMusic" parameter is only used to lower the volume of the Asynced lead sound when it transitions from "Stage 2" into the BossDeath loop. Before it continued to play in the boss loop so this was how I solved it. Probably not the way to go.
